# ---- Google Gemini (Google AI Studio) ----
# 1. Get a free API key: https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
# 2. Copy this file to  backend/.env  and paste your key below.
# 3. Restart the backend. The sidebar will show "Gemini AI online".
#
# Without a key the platform still runs fully on its built-in ML/rule engines.

GEMINI_API_KEY=

# Optional overrides:
# GEMINI_MODEL=gemini-2.5-flash
# GEMINI_API_BASE=https://generativelanguage.googleapis.com/v1beta
